data.description: MAGNIFICENT MUST SEE HOME!  You will fall in love with this home: 3 bed, 3 bath, Office Space, Loft, 3-car tandem garage on an oversized/landscaped corner lot. After entering from the COVERED PORCH, walk into a spacious FOYER; perfect for a future drop zone. The dedicated OFFICE SPACE, could be an extra nonconventional bedroom, is to your left. All main floor is SOLID SURFACE flooring and has the perfect OPEN CONCEPT floor plan. The living room has a  CUSTOM STONE FIREPLACE.  This is a  CHEF'S KITCHEN!  Enjoy a GAS RANGE, AMPLE GRANITE countertops, a breakfast BAR, and a PANTRY, which has dedicated lighting and solid shelves for perfect storage.  There is a DINING AREA with easy access to the exterior yard of the home. Upper level has a LARGE LOFT which is an ADDITIONAL LIVING ROOM or RECREATIONAL AREA as it is spacious enough for a pool table. And, the UPGRADED PLUSH CARPET is magnificent! There are many windows upstairs which are slightly tinted to give you extra privacy along with protection from hot summer days. The PRIMARY SUITE has enough room for a sitting area, and adjoints to an ENSUITE-5PIECE bathroom: SOAKING TUB, FULL SIZED SHOWER with TWO BENCHES & WALK-IN closet.  All granite matches in the home for seamless style. Additionally, the upstairs includes 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom, laundry room & extra storage closets. The 3-CAR TANDEM garage is perfect for a workshop as the walls are finished and is connected to the WHOLE HOUSE SURROUND SOUND.  The backyard is a true retreat with a shed, a paved walkway, grill area, UPGRADED TURF; xeriscaped with trees, flowers, etc.  This is PRIVACY at its best. Additional upgrades: gas meter, fiberoptics, spigots, surround sound, exterior paint, house humidifier, plantation blinds in primary bedroom, extra counter space in laundry room, storm doors on both doors, 1/4 acre lot, established trees.  Perfect location to shopping, schools, PETERSON & SCHRIEVER and more!  DON'T MISS THIS OPPORTUNITY
